{"tid":402800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又釋法？】12大專學生會聯署聲明 指討論港獨無違《基本法》 符合第27條","createTime":"2017-09-16T16:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T01:29:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b92949df77f7618694d6f8f4341e0e3b8f486b","tid":402800,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"【封殺民主牆】12大專學生會聯署聲明 指討論港獨無違《基本法》<br />\n<br />\n2017-09-16 22:38:41 HKT<br />\n<br />\n大學校園港獨爭議未停，8間資助大學聯同公開大學、樹仁大學，共10間大學校長昨日（15日）發表聯署聲明反對港獨，指港獨違反《基本法》。12間大專院校學生會今發聯署聲明指校方不支持港獨，但大學生師生享有討論港獨的言論自由，促請校方停止混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n12間大專院校學生會，包括城巿大學、恒生管理學院、浸會大學、科技大學、<br />\n嶺南大學、珠海學院、高等教育科技學院、教育大學、香港大學、公開大學、<br />\n樹仁大學及中文大學，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯署聲明指討論港獨絕對符合《基本法》第二十七條，有權作出討論。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，香港前途關注組在其facebook指已去信英國愛丁堡大學學生會，就該校候任校長馬斐森，昨聯署譴責港獨言論表達不滿。關注組指信中亦有建議該校生會，公開要求馬斐森確保愛丁堡大學校園內有討論香港獨立，以及蘇格蘭獨立的自由。他們認為一種行為違法，並不代表討論有關行為亦屬違法，舉例指不少中學辯論比賽都以安樂死為題。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"a74253305d06fc3d4e163bf33615e98cb375f20b","tid":402800,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588dc2e76c6bf78ab4f794fbcc4098adb6592f7d","tid":402800,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:38:40.000Z","msg":"第二十七條&nbsp;<br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"9c5f33ea0802fab21fc3e071f89152c8d5970c79","tid":402800,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"基本法第27條保障言論自由<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第二十七條規定，香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。據了解，聯署的醫生諮詢法律意見後，認為醫委會專業守則限制醫生自我宣傳的條文，可能違反上述《基本法》保障港人的權利，並可能牴觸人權法，<span style=\"color: red;\">法律意見又指言論自由應只在涉及誹謗、危害國家安全或社會秩序時才受限制</span>，醫生宣揚個人資料應不受此限。&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20051007/5289906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20051007%2F5289906&d=0bIx3vIRvviQG3QSfp0nIUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=4252de89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20051007%2F5289906&h=1b0f48f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20051007/5289906</a>"},{"pid":"1069385e874ffdff3c7193eef3bec90ec985eb63","tid":402800,"uid":33890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ofqc2sWRkFA/Wb1ICCf38KI/AAAAAAAAAdA/MrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs/s1600/wide_facebook.056.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ofqc2sWRkFA%2FWb1ICCf38KI%2FAAAAAAAAAdA%2FMrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fwide_facebook.056.png&h=b997e91a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c77953df81d4b5e168b6234ac969c288909e8193","tid":402800,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ofqc2sWRkFA/Wb1ICCf38KI/AAAAAAAAAdA/MrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs/s1600/wide_facebook.056.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ofqc2sWRkFA%2FWb1ICCf38KI%2FAAAAAAAAAdA%2FMrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fwide_facebook.056.png&h=b997e91a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b761d58d235f14613e912d429b2ac19b9fcf9a","tid":402800,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:56:11.000Z","msg":"細心睇《校長聲明》, 其實都無話唔比討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg&h=76655ef6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd1b2c121329620417413c305b2c7d4407da8a14","tid":402800,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ofqc2sWRkFA/Wb1ICCf38KI/AAAAAAAAAdA/MrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs/s1600/wide_facebook.056.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ofqc2sWRkFA%2FWb1ICCf38KI%2FAAAAAAAAAdA%2FMrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fwide_facebook.056.png&h=b997e91a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">支那國既「七不講」！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a7c60376b6137e919c602a8d964fdff14b8aa5e","tid":402800,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"係時候劃條線 封你門"},{"pid":"bb209e59d34793d329c034298e07c0b45354567d","tid":402800,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"跟著23條立法"},{"pid":"834756a95c9c33377bf557dd6fbd8e5300345c96","tid":402800,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:06:02.000Z","msg":"跟著本地23條立法"},{"pid":"58ff2bb3f2e88eb512b85c438b39c9603fa49632","tid":402800,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細心睇《校長聲明》, 其實都無話唔比討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg&h=76655ef6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心覺得佢地只係做比上面睇<br />\n佢地連自己個名都冇寫上去<br />\n佢地愈出黎講禁 只會不停搞大件事 <br />\n唔講過兩日就冇人記得<br />\n校長們應該冇咁蠢掛?!"},{"pid":"df9b3dc50cb8f2ecabc734a6e29a32696b7b34a1","tid":402800,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細心睇《校長聲明》, 其實都無話唔比討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg&h=76655ef6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心覺得佢地只係做比上面睇<br />\n佢地連自己個名都冇寫上去<br />\n佢地愈出黎講禁 只會不停搞大件事 <br />\n唔講過兩日就冇人記得<br />\n校長們應該冇咁蠢掛?!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漢字版：<br />\n我們珍惜言論自由，但我們譴責最近濫用言論自由的行為。言論自由並非絕對，有自由就有責任。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">=&gt; 遣責緊共匪向佢地施壓 及共媒鳩UP </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所有下列的大學，特此聲明，不支持「港獨」，並認為這是違反基本法。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> =&gt; 違反&quot;現在&quot;的基本法 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講出黎既說話唔係重點, 無講既說話先係重點<br />\n<br />\n校長無講D乜?<br />\n(1) 校長無講話校園唔准講港獨<br />\n(2) 校長無講話基本法唔可以條改<br />\n(3) 校長無講話港獨唔合理 / 唔可能<br />\n(4) 校長無講「不支持「港獨」」既理由, 係被迫定係點<br />\n(5) 前後兩句說話係分開,  校長無講「港獨」係「濫用言論自由」. 校長無講「濫用言論自由」實際係指D乜<br />\n(6)  校長無講「有自由就有責任」入面既責任係乜野責任。若果行使港獨的言論自由, 校長要求大家有責任實際行動？"},{"pid":"8e7085ae13dfebe963b763375f5f425301dec05f","tid":402800,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ofqc2sWRkFA/Wb1ICCf38KI/AAAAAAAAAdA/MrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs/s1600/wide_facebook.056.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ofqc2sWRkFA%2FWb1ICCf38KI%2FAAAAAAAAAdA%2FMrJsNrrffVknusJCbvWJa-jfEiRyZGPTgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fwide_facebook.056.png&h=b997e91a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">支那國既「七不講」！</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b9ea43ec4fa744acef3ad4faf4966d742bd601","tid":402800,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kung-15_DKqy6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkung-15_DKqy6_1200x0.png&h=ed7f6bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image94.360doc.com/DownloadImg/2016/02/1813/66232809_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage94.360doc.com%2FDownloadImg%2F2016%2F02%2F1813%2F66232809_5.jpg&h=cbd3ac95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c0913677332fafe51284d0ce6d8bdb7319c4e2f","tid":402800,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kung-15_DKqy6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkung-15_DKqy6_1200x0.png&h=ed7f6bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.blogchina.com/artpic_upload/y/e/z/yezijxp2015/65301427448814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.blogchina.com%2Fartpic_upload%2Fy%2Fe%2Fz%2Fyezijxp2015%2F65301427448814.jpg&h=fe301efb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大公報炮打司令部</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f8293fe5d87fb689846c4f2e3ba98916be0e131","tid":402800,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T17:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細心睇《校長聲明》, 其實都無話唔比討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg&h=76655ef6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心覺得佢地只係做比上面睇<br />\n佢地連自己個名都冇寫上去<br />\n佢地愈出黎講禁 只會不停搞大件事 <br />\n唔講過兩日就冇人記得<br />\n校長們應該冇咁蠢掛?!</blockquote><br />\n班校長本身有幾個以前先話支持學生<br />\n老實講要投共都無可能咁快 仲要一齊出聲明 擺明就係被施壓<br />\n不占我相信沈祖堯係真心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad0ce01444a333ebb3b84376d3402e07435fc08","tid":402800,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細心睇《校長聲明》, 其實都無話唔比討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F220147_3f127d7e7d0f42b566397bd59be09e1e.jpg&h=76655ef6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心覺得佢地只係做比上面睇<br />\n佢地連自己個名都冇寫上去<br />\n佢地愈出黎講禁 只會不停搞大件事 <br />\n唔講過兩日就冇人記得<br />\n校長們應該冇咁蠢掛?!</blockquote><br />\n班校長本身有幾個以前先話支持學生<br />\n老實講要投共都無可能咁快 仲要一齊出聲明 擺明就係被施壓<br />\n不占我相信沈祖堯係真心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聯合聲明咁撚短<br />\n<br />\n擺明就係好多野係無共識<br />\n<br />\n能夠有共識既野, 都留在好多空間去各自表述<br />\n<br />\n無講既野, 就係重點, 就係校長之間無共識既事黎"},{"pid":"f419b4025e1638dfd8cf73f0f3a17f1b9bc30371","tid":402800,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T18:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>